{"tid":1572770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「全民武裝」義士武裝大幅提升","createTime":"2019-09-15T18:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T18:27:34.000Z","uid":258814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f4cbbea1d2d1a917d482cdb12138960ae62c74d2","tid":1572770,"uid":258814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:26:09.000Z","msg":"雖然P牌仔，但有時間希望大家都睇睇<br />\n想大家可以投個票<br />\n依家局勢不明朗，但已經水深火熱<br />\n對家把刀已經「寒」住我地條頸<br />\n但我地依然赤手空拳，係唔係應該持武反抗？<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n讚同拎架餐作戰 =Like / 我和理非唔想見紅 =unlike<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我相信仲有好多和理非/口講憤怒但未敢突破框架成為落手既人存在，而班人應該好多時都講好想拎刀斬死曬班警同黑，再吾係就話想自己/叫人拎炸彈自殺式襲擊咁炸死佢地，如果依班人真係惡起上黎，痴撚線。所以！見到有人要開拖既吾好問只要狠狠咁打就實無死！Hit完要就好快趣Run啦<br />\n今日大家睇到一堆堆咁順暢既事，係唔係覺得硬係差少少野咁？<br />\n無錯，就係對家雖然比手足打傷，但<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「未見夠紅！仲企到起身」</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲未平熄我地個怒氣啊<br />\n咁撚輕手，<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點對得住之前被人斬腳既，被人打到爆紅既，被人非禮被人抽水既</span></strong>，依家吾清算，幾時啊？"},{"pid":"dc071c1c0fa4eaa8f819ec1ad6ed4d276cb200f5","tid":1572770,"uid":258814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:26:52.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"2e57c5f8ed953acda64a7db5b6bade4c95f356e5","tid":1572770,"uid":258814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:27:13.000Z","msg":"自推 2/10"},{"pid":"e093a994c87cc8a777928887387d32e82dde4cf8","tid":1572770,"uid":258814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"自推 3/10"},{"pid":"f550cc0286b7de39